## Benefits for your newsletter

This feature enables your subscribers to:

- **Gift subscriptions to friends or family** — Purchase subscriptions as birthday or holiday gifts
- **Corporate gifting** — Buy subscriptions for team members or clients
- **Support creators** — Purchase subscriptions for others who might enjoy your newsletter

